# No em dashes

Do not use em dashes (`—`, U+2014) anywhere in this repo: site copy, front matter, templates, README, scripts, or comments.

Use instead:

- ` | ` or ` · ` for title or label separators
- `, ` or `. ` to join clauses
- `-` (hyphen) for decorative breaks or comment asides
- `: ` after labels in docs

Before finishing edits, search for `—` and remove any matches.
